🔹 Introduction
Digital literacy is an essential skill in today’s technology-driven world. This project aims to develop practical knowledge of digital tools, online platforms, professional communication, and cyber safety. As a student digital ambassador, the objective was to promote responsible and effective use of digital resources.
The project involves creating an infographic, building a digital portfolio using platforms like GitHub, LinkedIn, and Kaggle, solving coding problems, designing a Google Form for data collection, and studying cybercrime awareness. Through these activities, I gained hands-on experience in managing digital content, communicating professionally, and understanding online risks.
