Objective:
To visually represent key concepts of digital literacy.
Work Done:
An infographic was created using Canva covering:
•	Digital literacy fundamentals 
•	Useful digital tools 
•	Safe internet practices 
•	Email etiquette 
•	Professional online presence 
Tools Used: Canva
Learning Outcome:
This task enhanced my ability to present information visually and improved my understanding of how different aspects of digital literacy are interconnected. One challenge faced was organizing multiple topics within limited space while maintaining clarity.
